OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,6,Fpossible at first, but soon clouding
OL,7,Fover with showery outbreaks of rain,
OL,8,Fthese turning heavy in places in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Much less warm than Friday.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will remain cloudy through
OL,12,Fthe evening and overnight with some
OL,13,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, heavy at
OL,14,Ffirst, gradually easing overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FDull, cool and cloudy through
OL,17,Fthe morning with a few light showers.
OL,18,FSome brighter spells may develop later
OL,19,Fin the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
