OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRain
OL,6,Ffor a time on Monday then bright
OL,7,Fspells and a few showers continuing
OL,8,Fthrough Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,9,FRemaining cooler with some overnight
OL,10,Ffrost.
